definition: surname Zou/vassal state during the Zhou Dynasty (1046-256 BC) in the southeast of Shandong Province

sentences.english: Mencius was born in Zou State, a very little country in modern day Shandong Province.
sentences.chinese: 孟子出生在邹县，是现在山东省一个非常小的地方。
